<TEXT>
Electrolux, the world's leading maker of household appliances, has taken a 6
per cent stake in Refripar, Brazil's second-largest producer of white goods,
in a strategic move to increase its presence in the South American white
goods market.
Electrolux is paying Dollars 10m for the stake, which will underpin an
