distribute household appliances under the Electrolux, Zanussi and Frigidaire
brand names.
Refripar, with 1993 sales of more than Dollars 350m, has a 50 per cent
market share in Brazil for freezers, and a 35 per cent share of the
refrigerator market. However, it is weak in washing machines.
Electrolux sales in South America were SKr2.4bn (Dollars 315.8m) last year,
but were mostly accounted for by floor cleaners.
