Lakeland and other shareholders totalling 112,679 ordinary and 62,613
preference shares, amounting to 71.6 per cent and 48.3 per cent of the
shares in issue.
Lakeland offers textile rental and laundry services. In the year to March 31
1994 pre-tax profits were Pounds 342,000 on turnover of Pounds 16.6m. Net
assets at the end of the period Pounds 5.1m.
