FT  13 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Emerald Energy Pounds 25,765 in profit
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Emerald Energy, the Isle of Man-based energy producer which obtained a USM
quote last November, reported a pre-tax profit of Pounds 25,765 for the six
months to end-March, against a loss of Pounds 15,738.
