Earnings per share came to 0.01p, against losses of 0.15p.
In April this year, Emerald raised Pounds 660,000 through a placing of 25m
shares to provide funds for acquisitions and its refurbishment programme.
It also acquired three gas fields in the Appalachian Basin for Dollars
475,000 (Pounds 312,000).
