FT  13 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Dwyer makes Pounds 4.8m property sale
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Dwyer Estates, the Irish property investment and trading group, has sold
Porterbrook House in Sheffield to Great Portland Estates for Pounds 4.8m.
