profits of Jacques Vert, the ladies' fashionwear group, doubled to Pounds
2.09m for the 53 weeks ended April 30. This compared with Pounds 1.03m last
time.
Earnings per share expanded from 8.8p to 13.45p while the dividend is
stepped up 50 per cent to 4.5p (3p) with a final payment of 3p.
