</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   From K A WILLSON
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Sir, The letter from Ambassador Pankin (July 4) should at least have
addressed the original problem created by his country's previous leaders,
namely the subjugation of the Latvian peoples and the deliberate Russian
'colonisation' by the injection of non-Latvian permanent residents.
K A Willson,
